data.description: LOCATION,LOCATION,LOCATION! This CHARMING 5 BEDROOM and 3 BATHROOMS home located in Downtown Homewood is just what you have been looking for. Close to parks, transportation, shopping and Award winning HF Schools. Three bedrooms on main level, private primary bedroom on lower level, and a bedroom in the finished basement. Updates throughout with lots of storage. Stainless steel appliances and gorgeous hardwood floors on main level. New garage and exterior doors in 2022. The home also is beautifully landscape and great for entertaining. Seller  is offering a $6000 credit for a new drive way.
